metadata.title: Prince William Sound Meteorological Buoy (Chlorophyll data)

creators.name: University of Alaska Fairbanks (UAF), School of Fisheries
Ocean Sciences (SFOS), Institute of Marine Science (IMS)

metadata.description:
Frequency
12 -18 times per day

Measurement Details
Sea Tech fluorometer

Geographic Area
Prince William Sound -  60 deg 36.3 min N ;  147 deg 12.2 min W
Other Comments
buoy is removed for the months of January and February.

Base Internet/URL ( http://murre.ims.alaska.edu:8000/~eslinger )  ( http://murre.ims.alaska.edu:8000/~eslinger/CLAB/clab.html )  

[ A TCODE project ]
